{
  "text": "From the measurements, it is evident that both films are less dense than bulk graphite and that between the carbon films the thinner one named S2 is the densest. Analysis using Leptos® software gives respectively for S1 and S2 a volumetric mass density, XRR  , of 1.47±0.05 g/cm [CITATION_1] and of 1.95±0.05 g/cm [CITATION_2] (see table 2 ).",
